mated to be 2 pi H, with H being the\nnominal disc scale height.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Dec 2008 20:57:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Dec 2008 01:38:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2009 18:02:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2009 10:36:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
