eflect an essential difference between discrimination\nfor two-states and multi-states. (4) A number of examples are constructed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Dec 2008 14:12:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Dec 2008 16:23:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2009 18:03:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2009 22:31:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-29"}
